{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-87-prime-power-triples","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 87: Tri osnovna broja sa snagom","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Najmanji broj koji se može predstaviti kao zbir kvadrata osnovnih brojeva, kub osnovnog broja i četvrti stepen osnovnog broja je <code>28</code>. Zapravo, postoji samo četiri broja ispod pedeset koji se mogu tako predstaviti:</p>\n<div style='margin-left: 4em;'>\n  28 = 2<sup>2</sup> + 2<sup>3</sup> + 2<sup>4</sup><br>\n  33 = 3<sup>2</sup> + 2<sup>3</sup> + 2<sup>4</sup><br>\n  49 = 5<sup>2</sup> + 2<sup>3</sup> + 2<sup>4</sup><br>\n  47 = 2<sup>2</sup> + 3<sup>3</sup> + 2<sup>4</sup>\n</div><br>\n<p>Koliko brojeva ispod <code>n</code> može se predstaviti kao zbir kvadrata osnovnog broja, kubusa osnovnog broja i četvrte moći osnovnog broja?</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3c51000cf542c50fed8","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302201,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-87-prime-power-triples"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function primePowerTriples(n) {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nprimePowerTriples(50);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>primePowerTriples(50)</code> trebalo bi da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof primePowerTriples(50) === 'number');"},{"text":"<p><code>primePowerTriples(50)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>4</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(primePowerTriples(50), 4);"},{"text":"<p><code>primePowerTriples(10035)</code> treba da vrati <code>684</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(primePowerTriples(10035), 684);"},{"text":"<p><code>primePowerTriples(500000)</code> treba da vrati <code>18899</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(primePowerTriples(500000), 18899);"},{"text":"<p><code>primePowerTriples(5000000)</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>138932</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(primePowerTriples(5000000), 138932);"},{"text":"<p><code>primePowerTriples(50000000)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>1097343</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(primePowerTriples(50000000), 1097343);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-1-to-100","dashedName":"problem-87-prime-power-triples","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-88-product-sum-numbers","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-86-cuboid-route","id":"5900f3c51000cf542c50fed8","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function arrangedProbability(limit) {\n  // Based on https://www.mathblog.dk/project-euler-100-blue-discs-two-blue/\n  let blue = 15;\n  let discs = 21;\n\n  while (discs < limit) {\n    const nextBlue = 3 * blue + 2 * discs - 2;\n    const nextDiscs = 4 * blue + 3 * discs - 3;\n\n    blue = nextBlue;\n    discs = nextDiscs;\n  }\n  return blue;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-87-prime-power-triples"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMa